title: Old launcher .exe needed!
body: Hi, im looking for old launcher (lol.launcher.exe/lol.launcher.admin.exe). For what i need it? Old launcher is the fastest way to fix any problems with new launcher (just delete new one and open old). I will be grateful.

replies.body: What kind of issues were you having that you wanted to try one of the old fixes that worked in the past? Should still have a few options to get this fixed up rather than trying to use an outdated client.
